<p>This demonstration page showcases the Ajax Fetch component's ability to load content asynchronously using Ajax calls, thereby enhancing user experience by eliminating the need for full page reloads.</p>

<h2>Example: Loading HTML Content</h2>

<div id="ajax-content-container">
    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-ajax-fetch='{"url":"https://example.com/content.html", "dataType":"html"}'>
        Load HTML Content
    </button>
    <div class="content-placeholder mrgn-tp-md">
        <p>Content will be loaded here upon clicking the button above.</p>
    </div>
</div>

